{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"db288cca12","title":"827 指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6f5dded986","index":0,"year":1967,"month":8,"day":27,"articleId":"db288cca12","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"许世友","id":"c2f8307fbd","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961-1968卷）（1968年武汉版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui5a.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"fb9330f296","type":"title","text":"827 指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"db288cca12","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"945b86ea06","type":"paragraph","text":"一、许世友要帮助过关，他是一个战将，文化革命以来，落后了，跟不上；","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"db288cca12","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cf7d451259","type":"paragraph","text":"二、要出马恩列斯语录；","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"db288cca12","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c58f62b7da","type":"paragraph","text":"三、文化大革命要搞三年，一年发动一年胜利，一年扫尾；","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"db288cca12","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e1f23414f1","type":"paragraph","text":"四、天津南开大学卫东红卫兵写了一篇好文章（指《要大胆使用革命干部》），提出了一个新问题，红卫兵小报是好东西；","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"db288cca12","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a57e9bc170","type":"paragraph","text":"五、不要把党内一小撮走资派和军内一小撮走资派并提，只提党内一小撮。把解放军搞垮了还要不要政府？","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"db288cca12","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d1934b781c","type":"paragraph","text":"六、群众组织提以我为核心，这样提是极蠢的；","index":6,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"db288cca12","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"164613c61a","type":"paragraph","text":"七、依靠青年人；","index":7,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"db288cca12","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"838d794ce5","type":"paragraph","text":"八、依靠群众，加强专政，新疆办大型劳改农场不一定好，要研究；","index":8,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"db288cca12","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"74b54e04af","type":"paragraph","text":"九、要抓学习，把工作做好，要精兵简政。","index":9,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"db288cca12","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":625,"end":625}}}},"__N_SSG":true}